idden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 06, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ouq1723639706136.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ouq1723639706136.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ouq1723639706136.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ouq1723639706136\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The [webentitywidgets] section of the initialization file contains logical widget\n\t\tdefinitions for entities used in Dynamic Server Page (DSP) components.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ouq1723639706136__topic_d147197e1_d147198e1_d147199e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ouq1723639706136__d6344e17\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">LogicalWidgetName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">PhysicalWidgetName</var>{<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">WidgetProperty1</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value1</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">;</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">WidgetProperty2</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Value2</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">;</code>...<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ouq1723639706136__topic_d106082e1_d106083e1_d106084e1_d106085e1_d106086e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1056728e96\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ouq1723639706136__p_d147206e1_d147207e1_d147208e1\">Each logical widget maps to a physical widget,\n\t\t\t\tand optionally sets some of its properties. The property values defined in this\n\t\t\t\tsection override the hard-coded defaults of the physical widget.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ouq1723639706136__p_d147209e1_d147210e1_d147211e1\">The maximum length of the widget property string\n\t\t\t\tis 1024 characters.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ouq1723639706136__p_d147212e1_d147213e1_d147214e1\">You can use this section to define your own\n\t\t\t\tlogical widgets for entities.</p>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"ouq1723639706136__pre_kmf_mbv_jcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[webentitywidgets]\n;  Logical to physical mapping of entity widget for DSPs\n\n  custom-Entity=customEntity\n\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8421653\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_8421653\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "[webentitywidgets] Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 06, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The [webentitywidgets] section of the initialization file contains logical widget definitions for entities used in Dynamic Server Page (DSP) components. LogicalWidgetName = PhysicalWidgetName { ( WidgetProperty1 = Value1 ; WidgetProperty2 = Value2 ; ... ) } Description Each logical widget maps to a physical widget, and optionally sets some of its properties. The property values defined in this section override the hard-coded defaults of the physical widget. The maximum length of the widget property string is 1024 characters. You can use this section to define your own logical widgets for entities. [webentitywidgets] ; Logical to physical mapping of entity widget for DSPs custom-Entity=customEntity Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}